    "created_at": "2016-04-08T05:28:54Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-04-08T05:28:54Z",
    "body": "This would leak processes, I think we can follow Chromium's behavior, by launching a background killer for the process:\n\n``` c++\n  base::Process process = base::LaunchProcess(argv, options);\n  if (process.IsValid())\n    base::EnsureProcessGetsReaped(process.Pid());\n```\n\nhttps://code.google.com/p/chromium/codesearch#chromium/src/chrome/browser/platform_util_linux.cc&q=XDGUtil&sq=package:chromium&type=cs&l=46\n"
  },
