    "updated_at": "2016-04-08T07:49:13Z",
    "body": "Thanks @zcbenz, good catch.\n\n@paulcbetts I've verified the fix like this:\n\n**Steps to reproduce:**\n- Make Firefox your default browser\n- Ensure all Firefox windows are closed\n- Start electron without no app\n- Click the \"docs\" link to launch Firefox\n- Go back to the electron window and attempt to select some text\n\n**Before PR**\nElectron window is frozen, text cannot be selected.\nClosing the Firefox window unfreezes the Electron window.\n\n**After PR**\nElectron window is not frozen, text can be selected, links clicked, etc.\n"
